3–502.
(a) Collective bargaining shall include all matters relating to:
(1) wages, hours, FRINGE BENEFITS OTHER THAN PENSION BENEFITS,
HEALTH BENEFITS, and other terms and conditions of employment; and
(2) the time and manner of access to a new employee program in
accordance with § 22–207 of the State Government Article.
